</media>
<para id="fs-idm188106160">The company can only perform 12,000 set-ups each period yet there is unlimited demand for each product. What is the differential profit from producing product E instead of product F for the year?</para>
<list id="fs-idm196776576" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>$216,000</item>
<item>$204,000</item>
<item>$12,000</item>
