<section id="fs-idm216238528" class="problem-set-a">
<exercise id="fs-idm201165152">
<problem id="fs-idm209788560">
<para id="fs-idm194530144"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68086"/>At Gems in the Rough, a jewelry company, the engraving department is a bottleneck. The company is considering hiring an extra worker, whose salary will be $56,000 per year, to ease the problem. Using the extra worker, the company will be able to engrave 8,000 more units per year. The selling price per unit is $16. The cost per unit currently is $11.85 as shown:</para>
